# convert English text into simple XML
# marking.m.elly
#

&@’ll -> \\1 will
&@’re -> \\1 are
&@n’t -> \\1 not
&@’ve -> \\1 have
&@’d  -> \\1 had
i'm   -> i am
he -’s  -> he is
it -’s  -> it is
here -’s  -> here is
@here -’s  -> \\1here is
that -’s  -> that is

1 another -> one another

, @&@ing that -> ,\\s\\1ing that
," @&@ing that -> ",\\s\\1ing that
,” @&@ing that -> ",\\s\\1ing that

. . . -> …
...   -> …
